-- London Marathon Reviewing Security for Next Weekend’s Race
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2013-04-15T20:49:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-15/london-marathon-reviewing-security-for-next-weekend-s-race.html
London Marathon and the city’s
police are reviewing the security of next weekend’s race in the
British capital after explosions at the Boston Marathon.  “Our security plan is developed jointly with the
Metropolitan Police and we were in contact with them as soon as
we heard the news,” London Marathon Chief Executive Officer
Nick Bitel said today in an e-mailed statement.   The London Marathon takes place April 21.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christopher Elser in London at 
 celser@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
